-- ============================================================
-- CIVILIZATION ROLE MAPPING (data-driven DLC support)
-- ============================================================
-- Maps civ names to Unit_Types keys for spawn and reinforcement.
-- Unknown DLC civs automatically fall back to default composition.
--
-- HOW TO ADD A NEW CIV:
--   1. Add Unit_Types entries above (start_player1_xxx, etc.)
--   2. Add the civ name to each map below
--   3. Done — Start_Setup & Reinforcements use these maps automatically
-- ============================================================

